title: #92Noon!  10am Hour 8/18 - Greg Papa, Ben Leber
description: 49ers radio voice Greg Papa is back on 92Noon for the second straight day for more shenanigans & football conversation. Plus, former Vikings linebacker Ben Leber joins the show to break down what he's seen from the purple & gold in the preseason.
